name: Ursula (The Little Mermaid) Disney by YeiyeiArt
description:
Ursula is a well-known Disney villain from The Little Mermaid. To create the Lora, a meticulously selected and refined DataSet was used to achieve a versatile and flexible model. So that it adapts perfectly to styles and models. It also works in 3D. Use the keyword “(UrsulaWaifu:1)” for greater precision, and I also recommend using the keywords “(dress), (short hair), (tentacles) / (tentacles instead legs), (scylla), (plump) to invoke her characteristic outfits. If you want to change her outfit, I recommend lowering the weight of the Lora between “0.8 - 0.5” for greater flexibility, I recommend use the negative tag (watermark:1.4), try it out and have fun. Remember to leave a Review with an image if you liked it and comment!! HAVE FUN :D

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. Currently Rapunzel, Snow White, Merida, Cinderella, Pocahontas, Fa Mulan, Elsa, Anna, Tiana and Alice in Wonderland, Ariel, Aurora!! From the Princess Series ;D” Also u have The Bonus Series with: Nani Pelekai, Lifeguard (lilo & stitch). And Tinker bell, Jane Porter (Tarzan). ToyStory: Jessie & Bo Peep.

Or

NEW !! Villain Collection: Maleficent.

NOTES: This version is more anime, if u want the ugly version of Ursula let me a comment and i can do a Update later <3

ADVICE!! “If you want a commission of something in particular, whether it’s a style or a character on request, contact me via email: jeanc.romero.ib@gmail.com.”
